{"tid":232722,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mr.A召喚] 裝唔到Linux","createTime":"2017-05-07T03:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T01:44:57.000Z","uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1e4028adb51eaa42eb21012b3c17cb0fa6d301","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T03:37:21.000Z","msg":"我而家用緊MacBook Pro 8,2 (15&quot;, early 2011)，想裝個Ubuntu 17.04玩dual boot<br />\n我跟住d tutorial 裝左rEFInd同分割左磁碟，但係唔知點解裝極都裝唔到ubuntu<br />\n我用隻燒左iso嘅usb boot機果陣，如果直接揀try ubuntu同install ubuntu，會變左黑mon乜反應都無，只可以長按開機掣強行閂機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我上網見到個方法叫我開機果陣㩒住option(alt)，入efi，係grub度㩒e去改boot parameter<br />\n<a href=\"https://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=2157775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fubuntuforums.org%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D2157775&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e4393ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=2157775</a><br />\n我照住佢講咁係段野最後加左下面d code<br />\noutb 0x728 1<br />\n outb 0x710 2<br />\n outb 0x740 2<br />\n outb 0x750 0<br />\n於是我成功入到ubuntu個桌面同埋安裝unbuntu(至少個電腦話install complete之類)<br />\n裝完部機就叫我重新開機，咁我就重開啦<br />\n但係佢一重開之後乜都無比我揀，自己直接變左紫色畫面(我諗係入左ubuntu)，個紫色mon同之前黑mon一樣完全無反應<br />\n<br />\n我應該點做先可以裝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f135c35858e0646da0d84687bd70a847b1f883a1","tid":232722,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"「你買部 mac 機做乜?」（Mr.A，2017）"},{"pid":"a281ac968e792b58331b0258e2b356b36f503033","tid":232722,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「你買部 mac 機做乜?」（Mr.A，2017）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe993fbb927b959880e62d8c05fec96f1f6b92c","tid":232722,"uid":42949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"linux都唔識裝<br />\n你邊有資格用linux<br />\n用返windows啦"},{"pid":"9ff1a5cfb653783e33cb7415b53383735d224d71","tid":232722,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"我裝linux會裝係usb手指到。"},{"pid":"1dcc024019a3984768f4db14e768e6384ef6f4d9","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"小弟電腦白痴，只係想試下轉linux，各位大佬有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e947eb6578a157e636e41edafd76b5dbb75c04","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我裝linux會裝係usb手指到。</blockquote><br />\n我怕自己用用下電腦會整跌隻手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以諗住都係dual os好似安全d"},{"pid":"d60e11bbe770f262f0d74b7a73fccce5acc06a2c","tid":232722,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟電腦白痴，只係想試下轉linux，各位大佬有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 virtual box 裝個 Linux 試下慣唔慣先得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be48fc9e5136f208c42f8b8f17e90392bfd5c387","tid":232722,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:25:17.000Z","msg":"try 時有冇好慢，上唔到網，窒窒下<br />\nboot 機時按 esc 有冇乜野 process fail 左"},{"pid":"8fafca0cc0a85c6cf1ae3551e06fc1f3f2f36a07","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟電腦白痴，只係想試下轉linux，各位大佬有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 virtual box 裝個 Linux 試下慣唔慣先得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果試多幾日都係搞唔掂我就用virtual machine (但係唔知我會唔會vm都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"8348f5579ab9be723c1b9f05a62087ade5849334","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>try 時有冇好慢，上唔到網，窒窒下<br />\nboot 機時按 esc 有冇乜野 process fail 左</blockquote><br />\ntry嘅時候幾順，本來search唔到wifi，我跟住上網教，入去system and software&gt;additional drive開返d disable左嘅野就連到wifi<br />\n<br />\nboot機esc之後去左個grub嘅畫面，我照返之前咁edit加outb 0x728 1...之後就成功入到ubuntu desktop<br />\n但係都係揾唔到wifi，不過今次我再去addtional drive發現佢乜野都無，無得好似之前咁比我取消disable<br />\n我用iwconfig，佢顯示<br />\neth0 no wireless extensions.<br />\nlo no wireless extentions.<br />\n<br />\n點解notebook佢都可以話我無wireless extionsion<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，聽日再試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee56a9ad6e3057b8e8904ace2752a1e38d30176f","tid":232722,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟電腦白痴，只係想試下轉linux，各位大佬有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 virtual box 裝個 Linux 試下慣唔慣先得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果試多幾日都係搞唔掂我就用virtual machine (但係唔知我會唔會vm都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVM 好簡單<br />\n我電腦白痴都搞得掂<br />\n你冇可能唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDown 個 ISO set 好 VM 之後仲易過 windows 10<br />\n應該網上有教學添<br />\n有問題再一齊研究啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5feb407041097f0fe794c474655cc0c29469fc15","tid":232722,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/187410/how-to-install-and-dual-boot-linux-on-a-mac/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2F187410%2Fhow-to-install-and-dual-boot-linux-on-a-mac%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=613e3951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.howtogeek.com/187410/how-to-install-and-dual-boot-linux-on-a-mac/</a><br />\n<br />\n琴晚跟住呢個做，但我果部係MACBOOK AIR 2014"},{"pid":"e91eb280815b92d87aacd4e996ffe3d9487a109e","tid":232722,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"岩岩裝左IBUS 速成，但個選字同windows唔同，有無巴打有計？"},{"pid":"cc5cc247d333d870eae712206885c6bd49fccc34","tid":232722,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩裝左IBUS 速成，但個選字同windows唔同，有無巴打有計？</blockquote><br />\n用倉頡"},{"pid":"6e097dd1bd61c86cf5adec0fc5f58b34ef223e88","tid":232722,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T01:34:06.000Z","msg":"17.04仲係唔係unity"},{"pid":"b81a41e77d45e81447170d47a7f7c411040d1870","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟電腦白痴，只係想試下轉linux，各位大佬有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 virtual box 裝個 Linux 試下慣唔慣先得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果試多幾日都係搞唔掂我就用virtual machine (但係唔知我會唔會vm都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVM 好簡單<br />\n我電腦白痴都搞得掂<br />\n你冇可能唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDown 個 ISO set 好 VM 之後仲易過 windows 10<br />\n應該網上有教學添<br />\n有問題再一齊研究啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家我dual boot到，不過每次boot機都要加d code先入到ubuntu，唔係就紫mon<br />\n等我搞掂埋個wifi應該正式用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4ca5ca2aeab621a5c41ddce719f12eb883691b","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/187410/how-to-install-and-dual-boot-linux-on-a-mac/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2F187410%2Fhow-to-install-and-dual-boot-linux-on-a-mac%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=613e3951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.howtogeek.com/187410/how-to-install-and-dual-boot-linux-on-a-mac/</a><br />\n<br />\n琴晚跟住呢個做，但我果部係MACBOOK AIR 2014</blockquote><br />\n我一開始都係跟呢個，但係因為install完ubuntu就卡住左"},{"pid":"ab5905cab72585c6f64b3c31966ea83fe82133a0","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>17.04仲係唔係unity</blockquote><br />\n我唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7e30350eb9506c99b15842d172e740bb825da0","tid":232722,"uid":59715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:42:13.000Z","msg":"Bootflag加nomodeset 試下"},{"pid":"aca1ab7f028c482e0b3d35c402fe4563dc1b6592","tid":232722,"uid":107001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T17:19:03.000Z","msg":"匯報返最新情況，多謝大家幫手，而家已經成功上到網，不過每次boot機都要加段code先入到ubuntu<br />\n同埋我發現用親ubuntu部機都好熱，而且個風扇好似唔識轉(正常呢個熱嘅程度，mac os應該會開個風扇開到好嘈)"},{"pid":"3c76d3622a05ff30b2c64ac11050b4085ed921a7","tid":232722,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"Mr.A<br />\n裝唔到Linux?<br />\n裝Linux啦"},{"pid":"e8f1cdd114813a7a09a79ad6c8a93f09832b9c87","tid":232722,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: brown;\">Installing Linux on a Mac, Why Bother? </span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.softpedia.com/news/installing-linux-on-a-mac-why-bother-488235.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.softpedia.com%2Fnews%2Finstalling-linux-on-a-mac-why-bother-488235.shtml&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c5b98933\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.softpedia.com/news/installing-linux-on-a-mac-why-bother-488235.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 係人都知MAC機機件獨特, macOS之外都好難搵到其他OS嘅合適drivers. 要裝Linux就裝係VM算啦, 唔好為難自己, 計我話! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a06b733e5ced660af9a401fa06176230e2b3b10","tid":232722,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: brown;\">Installing Linux on a Mac, Why Bother? </span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.softpedia.com/news/installing-linux-on-a-mac-why-bother-488235.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.softpedia.com%2Fnews%2Finstalling-linux-on-a-mac-why-bother-488235.shtml&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c5b98933\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.softpedia.com/news/installing-linux-on-a-mac-why-bother-488235.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 係人都知MAC機機件獨特, macOS之外都好難搵到其他OS嘅合適drivers. 要裝Linux就裝係VM算啦, 唔好為難自己, 計我話! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple 霸權咁無恥唔開 spec 唔出 Linux drivers <br />\n你哋班人視若無睹<br />\n總有一日烓到你度<br />\n<br />\n強力要求所有公司要 open hardware spec 同支持 Linux driver 研發<br />\n自己唔出都開 spec la 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b1acba40b8fdee021dcccbf8bf8e11f0867361","tid":232722,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>匯報返最新情況，多謝大家幫手，而家已經成功上到網，不過每次boot機都要加段code先入到ubuntu<br />\n同埋我發現用親ubuntu部機都好熱，而且個風扇好似唔識轉(正常呢個熱嘅程度，mac os應該會開個風扇開到好嘈)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣用Linux用到部MAC機燒咗就好笑喇! 何必呢?<br />\n(BTW, 明明macOS已經係個強大嘅Unix system嚟, 你反而要部機屈就去裝Linux, 其實係有啲反智! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"}]}